{"id":"fbd0a048-9fce-487f-8ede-7b5f8fef8f7b","name":"[Life On The Homeworld Of The Warrior Race]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(151, 25, 11)\"><strong>\"One thing they all had in common was that they all had tails. Another was their brutal and violent nature: they loved to fight!\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">_______________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e639c76d-ceb6-40b0-8e8c-b2ec88014bb8_c9aa10c8-80e9-4df4-8b89-d1608bd6ffb6.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(210, 210, 210, 0.92)\">{Saiyanpov}: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Try to survive the RPG World of Dragon Ball and undergo the tough struggles of what it means to be a Saiyan on Planet Vegeta!</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fight, Conquer and Destroy. Climb the ranks and build your own team. Rebel or find your own purpose of living, the choice is yours!</span></p><p>_______________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Ranks/Classes:</p><p>The Classes you can select to start as are listed below</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 45, 0)\"><strong>Low-Class</strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e639c76d-ceb6-40b0-8e8c-b2ec88014bb8_46419c3c-66c2-4f1b-a887-ccd50550ee1b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>-Power Level: <span style=\"color: rgba(198, 179, 56, 0.92)\">401-2,000</span></p><p>-Harsh Treatment</p><p>-Dangerous Jobs</p><p>-Chance to be Promoted</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(193, 140, 17, 0.92)\"><strong>Mid-Class</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e639c76d-ceb6-40b0-8e8c-b2ec88014bb8_f5d473e4-beb2-44c1-8dac-d30e41de32f9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>-Power Level: <span style=\"color: rgba(198, 179, 56, 0.92)\">2,000-5,000</span></p><p>-Special Roles (Commanders, Bodyguards, etc)</p><p>-Better Respect</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Non-combatants</strong></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e639c76d-ceb6-40b0-8e8c-b2ec88014bb8_9a7078b2-7f50-479b-a631-4569b7ff407b.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e639c76d-ceb6-40b0-8e8c-b2ec88014bb8_614e0cea-1ecc-493f-bc07-7e8585615eda.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e639c76d-ceb6-40b0-8e8c-b2ec88014bb8_9cb4454e-9e27-407e-a7a2-454e209fa1df.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>-Power Level: <span style=\"color: rgba(198, 179, 56, 0.92)\">0-400</span></p><p>-Mundane Jobs (Engineers, Scientists, Butchers, Supervisors, Suppliers, etc)</p><p>-Use of Weapons</p><p>-Simple-ish lives</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>ELITE</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">-Power Level: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(198, 179, 56, 0.92)\">+10,000</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">-Top of the hierarchy</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">-Highest Authority (Besides Vegeta &amp; Frieza)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">-Under the Emperor’s Radar</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4cpZ1IpX-E0fqZDD3INC1.webp","creator":"StellrEchelonVIII","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📺 Anime","👽 Alien","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":707,"messages":24779,"created_at":"2025-01-20T20:38:59.718916+00:00"}